Fig. 8C
). Mantle vesicles smooth but forming lobes (
Fig. 9C
). Tentacles and vesicles uniformly brown, tentacle tips round and white, oral disc green. In contrast to its congenerics, this species shows a remarkably consistent colouration among colonies

